## Step 6: Test

### Test AI extraction (enabled):
```bash
# Upload PDF with AI extraction
curl -X POST https://your-railway.app/api/omni/train \
  -F "file=@GET-204-Module-1-8.pdf"

# Check logs for:
# "[AI extraction completed successfully]"
# "First extracted fact: Establishments where raw wood..."
```

### Test regex fallback (disabled):
```bash
# Temporarily disable AI in Railway dashboard:
AI_EXTRACTION_ENABLED=false

# Redeploy or restart container

# Upload same PDF
curl -X POST https://your-railway.app/api/omni/train \
  -F "file=@GET-204-Module-1-8.pdf"

# Check logs for:
# "[Using regex extraction]"
# "First extracted fact: ment where raw wood..." (truncated)
```

### Test per-request override:
```bash
# Force AI for this request (even if env flag is false)
curl -X POST "https://your-railway.app/api/omni/train?ai=true" \
  -F "file=@GET-204-Module-1-8.pdf"

# Force regex for this request (even if env flag is true)
curl -X POST "https://your-railway.app/api/omni/train?ai=false" \
  -F "file=@GET-204-Module-1-8.pdf"
```

